Rating: 4
I didn't cut anything. It's a cake, not a health food! lol I had every intention of baking it just as written, but remembered I had a little piece of ginger in the fridge that needed to be used, so I added that. With or without the ginger, this would be a fabulous, dense cake. The icing was worrisome because it was so runny, so I (oh, no!!) added more powdered sugar. 8 oz. makes a lot of icing for a bundt cake. Next time, I'll use half, and keep the thin consistency. I'll be making this again.

