I used orange mango applesauce and 3 T. oil in lieu of 1 c. of oil. No pineapple, 3 small bananas and 2 medium carrots. Produced 22 moist medium and flavorable muffins baked at 350 for 16 minutes. Everyone (including teens) thought muffins were sweet except my husband who loves everything sickening sweet. No frosting needed if you are going the muffin route.

